      "date": "2012-11-01 05:26:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\n@@ -1664,9 +1823,12 @@ int mdt_close(struct mdt_thread_info *info)\r\n                 rc = err_serious(rc);\r\n         }\r\n\r\n+       LASSERT(req->rq_export != NULL);\r\n         med = &req->rq_export->exp_mdt_data;\r\n+       LASSERT(med != NULL);\r\n         cfs_spin_lock(&med->med_open_lock);\r\n         mfd = mdt_handle2mfd(info, &info->mti_ioepoch->handle);\r\n+       LASSERT(mfd != NULL);\r\n------------------------------ This line caused both recovery-small.test_23 and replay-single.test_14 failure.",
